    <p>For inquiries or to get started, please reach out to us:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email: <a href="mailto:info@jobagency.com">info@jobagency.com</a></li>
        <li>Phone: (123) 456-7890</li>
        <li>Address: 123 Job St, City, Country</li>
    </ul>
</div>

